                      "id": "v18MP6",
                      "name": "rc",
                      "fill": "#1D4ED8",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "Default to the Role matrix. It scans best, keeps accent fonts visible, and still gives a clear path into detailed editing.",
